{"tid":1513472,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO 平權兄弟 可否暫時靜下?","createTime":"2019-08-28T10:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T12:48:39.000Z","uid":20294,"like":9,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6f918e2a3528a6aa5b40f0a4e49218611fc023c6","tid":1513472,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:45:49.000Z","msg":"利申 手持BNO 非分化<br />\n<br />\n現階段 最重要係五大訴求<br />\n同時推動香港民主進程<br />\n抗赤化 保存香港獨有體制同地位<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候搞平權 感覺就似<br />\n<br />\n「我唔想係香港啦 比我走啦」<br />\n<br />\n「就算輸左 我都可以移民」<br />\n<br />\n既感覺<br />\n<br />\n但依家要<br />\n<br />\n「齊上齊落」<br />\n<br />\n200 萬+7 ,BNO 佔幾多% 大家有數得計<br />\n<br />\n根本就唔可以 係呢個時候 用小數利益著想<br />\n<br />\n大家要將文宣用力量 集中返係 五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n希望相關兄弟諗下 暫時以整為重 君為輕 三思"},{"pid":"fc68b8fb18eec388274286ada88527f346a593a4","tid":1513472,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:46:09.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 <br />\n<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"abddef0b6b10ca94fa122aeeaba3bfb5ebe1ee65","tid":1513472,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:46:20.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 <br />\n<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"3559c18fa8b02846ed2d630afd951ad173d67d5b","tid":1513472,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:46:35.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 <br />\n<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"a32b3668d9bf63ed276590b1ecfea61a95e06ae0","tid":1513472,"uid":19869,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:46:46.000Z","msg":"兩樣一齊做"},{"pid":"25fbbd440fcd90da501066ff3fb91eaa1ad7ab3e","tid":1513472,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:46:49.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 <br />\n<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"232af268e3589f6215a42c33ea0bdcd6aa13741e","tid":1513472,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:47:22.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"bed27cfe4328fc2a0c4d089716a0a085ad5defc2","tid":1513472,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cit